{"tid":1155291,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過隻狗唔肯食野","createTime":"2019-05-15T00:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T11:41:56.000Z","uid":41302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"68490f512273979c6599dd7455bee52f5b3e0849","tid":1155291,"uid":41302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:20:08.000Z","msg":"細狗大約大歲<br />\n係早一個月前突然間對糧食無曬興趣 <br />\n開頭以為係隻糧擺得耐走左味而唔食<br />\n突登買過一包都係咁<br />\n<br />\n以前一話開飯佢會好興奮 <br />\n到依家佢會去聞下食幾粒就走左去<br />\n可能擺成半粒鐘先食曬或者食一半<br />\n<br />\n佢屙屎正常 <br />\n試過比零食佢又會食得好快<br />\n<br />\n有無人知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a16a934afe2249bb4a0020e8f01d88cebc348bb","tid":1155291,"uid":14766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:21:11.000Z","msg":"我隻狗都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc974202cf553f4c5f050c76dcbd26e8a8385d9","tid":1155291,"uid":41302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a16a934afe2249bb4a0020e8f01d88cebc348bb","tid":1155291,"uid":14766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:21:11.000Z","msg":"我隻狗都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:23:01.000Z","msg":"持續左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔忍心見佢唔食野"},{"pid":"2ea8d53aa787648b4bd1b75195b949304c94b1d9","tid":1155291,"uid":41302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:23:38.000Z","msg":"打錯字 細狗大約歲半"},{"pid":"e45dac2b620ef05ab52002ea9a8664634c6b97db","tid":1155291,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:25:38.000Z","msg":"你地食飯成日比餸佢食<img src=\"/asset